# URL Shortener

The purpose of this project is to improve system design skills by building a URL shortener service.

## Project scope

The scope of this project consider the following:
* Allow to create shortened versions of long urls.
* Being redirect to the long url when short url is requested.
* Shortened urls should be as small as possible.
* The service are able to set a expire timestamp

## Technologies used

* PostgreSQL for storing the urls
* Redis for storing the most visited urls
* Actix for serving the http server
